; Test cube — 10mm x 10mm x 10mm, perimeters + solid top & bottom
; 20 layers @ 0.5mm layer height
; This file validates the full parser and surface extractor pipeline.
G90          ; absolute positioning
M82          ; absolute extrusion mode
G28          ; home all axes
G92 E0       ; reset extruder

; ── Bottom layer (Z = 0.5) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
G1 Z0.5 F600
G1 X0  Y0  E0   F1200
G1 X10 Y0  E0.5
G1 X10 Y10 E1.0
G1 X0  Y10 E1.5
G1 X0  Y0  E2.0
; Bottom infill
G1 X2  Y2  E2.3 F800
G1 X8  Y2  E2.6
G1 X8  Y4  E2.9
G1 X2  Y4  E3.2
G1 X2  Y6  E3.5
G1 X8  Y6  E3.8
G1 X8  Y8  E4.1
G1 X2  Y8  E4.4

